lead_paragraph: The feud between Jason Taylor and Bill Parcells intensified Wednesday, making it likely that Taylor, a six-time Pro Bowl defensive end, has played his last game for the Miami Dolphins. Coach Tony Sparano said Taylor was not expected to take part in team activities through camp. The revelation came less than 24 hours after Taylor finished second to Kristi Yamaguchi in the finals of “Dancing With the Stars” in Los Angeles.
